:markdown
  An experiment in HTML/CSS/JS solitaire. Play Klondike or Spider.

%div{ style: 'margin-top: 1em;' }
  .aspect-ratio
    %canvas{ :width => 6, :height => 5 }
    #card-experiments
      .options
        %form.load-game
          %label
            Load a new game:
            %input{ :type => "text", :name => "game", :list => "game_list", :pattern => "[a-z\-]+", :value => "spider", :title => "Alphanumeric characters and dashes only please!" }
          %datalist#game_list
            %option{ :value => "klondike" }
            %option{ :value => "spider" }
          %button{ :type => "submit" } New Game
        %form.full-screen
          %button{ :type => "submit" } Full Screen

:markdown
  Source is on [Github](https://github.com/ericfreese/ericfreese.github.io).

